0and%20then%20have%20a%20strike%20of%20118%20when%20you%20get%20out%20in%20the%2014th%20or%20the%2015th%20over%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20if%20you%20want%20applause%20for%20that%2C%20that's%20a%20little%20bit%20different.%20That's%20different%2C%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gavaskar%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20for%20Star%20Sports%20to%20show%20the%20person%20belittling%20their%20own%20commentators%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure%20that's%20a%20great%20thing.%20So%20I%20think%20Star%20Sports%20needs%20to%20understand%20that%20they%20have%20shown%20it%20enough%20times%2C%20everyone's%20got%20the%20message.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22et%5C%22%3EGavaskar%20owning%20kohli%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fg5j2WiVtJW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fg5j2WiVtJW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20'%20(%40Dhoniverse_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDhoniverse_%2Fstatus%2F1786778686772928988%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20stars%20like%20Kohli%20should%20not%20bother%20to%20respond%20on%20'outside%20noise'%20if%20they%20don't%20care%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20guys%20talk%20about%2C%20'oh%20we%20don't%20care%20about%20outside%20noise'.%20Accha!%20Then%20why%20are%20you%20replying%20to%20any%20outside%20noise%20or%20whatever%20it%20is.%20We%20all%20played%20a%20bit%20of%20cricket%2C%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket.%20We%20don't%20have%20agendas.%20We%20speak%20about%20what%20we%20see.%20We%20don't%20necessarily%20have%20any%20likes%20and%20dislikes.%20Even%20if%20we%20have%20likes%20and%20dislikes%2C%20we%20actually%20speak%20on%20what%20is%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESo%20according%20to%20Gavaskar%20saab%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20people%20cry%20on%20kohli%20everyday%20Kohli%20shouldn't%20reply%20his%20critics%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9yiAYtXrg8%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F9yiAYtXrg8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20POTT%20(%40KlolZone)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKlolZone%2Fstatus%2F1786760699634729056%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20skipper%20even%20criticised%20IPL's%20official%20broadcasters%20for%20showing%20Kohli's%20interview%20time%20and%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20Star%20Sports%20realises%20that%20when%20that%20clip%20is%20shown%2C%20questioning%20the%20critics%2C%20the%20critics%20are%20your%20own%20commentators.%20For%20you%20to%20show%20the%20person%20belittling%20your%20own%20commentators%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure%20that's%20a%20great%20thing.%20You%20need%20to%20realise%20you%20have%20shown%20it%20enough%20times%2C%20everybody's%20got%20the%20message.%20I%20would%20be%20very%20disappointed%20if%20you%20show%20it%20once%20more.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714846860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fl6adv8v8_kohli-gavaskar_625x300_04_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fangry-sunil-gavaskar-blasts-virat-kohlis-rant-says-dont-have-agenda-why-are-you-replying-to-outside-noise-5589368%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%20referred%20to%20an%20interview%20by%20Virat%20Kohli%20ahead%20of%20the%20RCB%20vs%20GT%20match%20on%20Saturday%20and%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Battleground%3A%20Contest%20Of%20Fine%20Margins%20Between%20BJP%2C%20Trinamool%20In%20Bengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal's%2042%20seats%20make%20it%20the%20third-largest%20contributor%20of%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20but%20what%20has%20made%20the%20state%20even%20more%20important%20and%20interesting%20in%20these%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20is%20the%20keenly%20fought%20contest%20between%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20neither%20side%20willing%20to%20give%20any%20quarter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20NDTV's%20special%20show%20'Battleground'%20on%20Saturday%2C%20hosted%20by%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%2C%20a%20panel%20of%20experts%20and%20spokespersons%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20TMC%20dissected%20every%20issue%20that%20could%20play%20a%20role%20in%20either%20party%20getting%20an%20upper%20hand%20and%20also%20shared%20their%20thoughts%20on%20what%20drives%20violence%20during%20elections%20in%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20-%20and%20a%20Presidential-style%20contest%20between%20them%20-%20dominated%20the%20discussion%2C%20the%20two%20other%20main%20points%20that%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20were%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20controversy%20and%20the%20welfare%20push%20by%20both%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%2C%20barring%20the%20spokespersons%20of%20course%2C%20seemed%20to%20agree%20that%20the%20contest%20in%20the%20state%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20neck%20and%20neck%20one%20and%20the%20battle%20is%20going%20to%20be%20one%20of%20fine%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20state's%2042%20seats%2C%2022%20were%20won%20by%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%202019%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20made%20huge%20inroads%20and%20achieved%20victory%20in%2018.%20Far%20from%20resting%20on%20its%20laurels%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20relentless%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20increase%20its%20vote%20share%20since%20then%2C%20but%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20also%20fought%20tooth%20and%20nail%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20its%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20how%20razor-thin%20the%20margins%20are%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20Professor%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%20(CSDS)%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWest%20Bengal%20is%20a%20state%20where%20the%20regional%20party%20is%20very%20strong%20but%20the%20BJP%20is%20putting%20up%20a%20fierce%20contest.%20The%20BJP%20has%20defeated%20the%20Congress%20in%20many%20states%20but%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20contesting%20against%20regional%20parties%2C%20but%20Bengal%20is%20an%20exception.%20I%20think%20there%20is%20a%20neck-and-neck%20fight.%20This%20is%20a%20battleground%20in%20the%20real%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20contest%20in%20every%20seat.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20difference%20in%20vote%20share%20between%20the%20parties%20was%20just%20three%20per%20cent.%20The%20difference%20in%20seats%20was%20also%20of%20only%20four.%20If%20the%20votes%20swing%20by%202%20per%20cent%20either%20way...%20if%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20goes%20up%20by%202-3%20per%20cent%2C%20the%20TMC%20can%20lose%207-8%20seats%20and%20if%20the%20opposite%20happens%20and%20the%20BJP%20loses%204-5%20per%20cent%20of%20votes%20it%20can%20be%20reduced%20to%20single%20digits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20this%20point%2C%20political%20strategist%20Amitabh%20Tiwari%20said%20there%20were%2022%20seats%20in%202019%20where%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20was%20less%20than%2010%25%20or%201%20lakh%20votes%20-%20and%20these%20were%20split%20evenly%20between%20the%20TMC%20and%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BSo%20there%20is%20definitely%20a%20'%3Cem%3Ekaante%20ki%20takkar'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20neck-and-neck-fight)%20and%20this%20has%20become%20a%20seat-by-seat%20contest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Violence%20Vitiates%20Society'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pugalia%20pointed%20out%20there%20is%20a%20dichotomy%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20while%20Bengal%20is%20considered%20a%20leader%20in%20terms%20of%20culture%20and%20self-respect%2C%20it%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20violent%20states%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20political%20violence.%20To%20this%2C%20political%20analyst%20Swapan%20Dasgupta%20said%20the%20violence%20is%20a%20legacy%20of%20the%20Left%2C%20which%20ruled%20Bengal%20for%20decades%20and%20even%20the%20Trinamool%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20this%20when%20it%20was%20fighting%20the%20CPM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20those%20rough-and-ready%20methods%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20have%20become%20the%20new%20normal%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20I%20think%20this%20is%20something%20that%2C%20regardless%20of%20which%20side%20you%20prefer%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20unanimity%20on%20stopping%20the%20violence.%20This%20vitiates%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20an%20interesting%20statistic%2C%20Mr%20Dasgupta%20said%20no%20national%20party%20has%20ever%20won%20a%20majority%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20West%20Bengal%20since%201971.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20caste%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20class%20-%20which%20was%20the%20CPM's%20dominant%20narrative%20-%20has%20made%20an%20entry%20in%20Bengal%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Important%20Is%20Sandeshkhali%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20important%20a%20role%20the%20issue%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20-%20where%20there%20have%20been%20allegations%20of%20land%20grab%2C%20rape%20and%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20a%20Trinamool%20strongman%20and%20his%20aides%20-%20will%20be%20in%20the%20elections%2C%20Amitabh%20Tiwari%20said%20this%20depends%20on%20how%20much%20the%20BJP%20can%20make%20it%20pervade%20the%20public%20consciousness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202019%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20the%20TMC%20had%20more%20of%20a%20lead%20against%20the%20BJP%20among%20women%20voters%20than%20among%20men.%20The%20lead%20was%20roughly%204%20per%20cent%20among%20women%20as%20against%202%20per%20cent%20among%20men.%20This%20issue%20could%20become%20important%20because%20support%20among%20women%20has%20been%20a%20strong%20point%20of%20the%20TMC%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mention%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20sparked%20a%20heated%20debate%20between%20TMC%20Spokesperson%20Riju%20Dutta%20and%20BJP%20Spokesperson%20and%20West%20Bengal%20State%20Secretary%20Priyanka%20Tibrewal%2C%20especially%20since%20Saturday%20was%20when%20a%20sting%20video%20by%20a%20private%20channel%20went%20viral%20in%20which%20a%20BJP%20leader%20purportedly%20says%20that%20no%20rapes%20or%20sexual%20harassment%20had%20taken%20place%20and%20women%20were%20convinced%20to%20file%20such%20complaints%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20senior%20party%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%2C%20Gangadhar%20Koyal%2C%20has%20claimed%20that%20his%20voice%20was%20edited%20and%20has%20also%20sent%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiring%20the%20first%20volley%2C%20Mr%20Dutta%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20%26quot%3Bnever%20understood%20and%20will%20never%20understand%20the%20diverse%2C%20pluralistic%2C%20democratic%20ethos%20of%20Bengal%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20sting%2C%20a%20BJP%20block%20president%20is%20saying%20that%20the%20party's%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20has%20paid%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20these%20women%20to%20file%20fake%20rape%20cases%20dating%207-8%20months%20back.%20Can%20you%20imagine%20what%20a%20concocted%20conspiracy%20this%20is%20to%20defame%20Bengal.%20The%20BJP%20can%20debate%20till%20the%20cows%20come%20home%20that%20this%20is%20morphed%20but%20this%20is%20what%20their%20leaders%20are%20saying%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Tibrewal%20countered%20that%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20had%20initially%20said%20that%20the%20victims%20were%20lying%20and%20alleged%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20may%20have%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20video%20went%20viral.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20has%20asked%20the%20CBI%20to%20probe%20this%20(Sandeshkhali%20allegations)%20and%2C%20in%20a%20hearing%20on%20Thursday%2C%20said%20there%20are%20similarities%20between%20the%20CBI%20report%20and%20the%20victims'%20affidavits.%20This%20shows%20that%20such%20incidents%20have%20taken%20place%20there.%20%C2%A0At%20least%20750%20affidavits%20were%20given%20and%20the%20TMC%20wants%20to%20say%20750%20people%20are%20lying.%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20talk%20of%20nari%20shakti%20(women%20power)%20stands%20exposed%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Pugalia%20asked%20pointedly%20whether%20something%20happened%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Mr%20Dutta%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMistakes%20were%20made%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20Excesses%20happened.%20But%20Sandeshkhali%20is%20a%20land%20issue.%20Some%20people%20misused%20the%20Trinamool%20symbol%20and%20grabbed%20land.%20But%20the%20politics%20being%20done%20on%20women's%20bodies%2C%20that%20never%20happened.%20That%20has%20been%20exposed%20today.%20We%20have%20suspended%20the%20Trinamool%20leader%20and%20others%20have%20been%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%20party%20but%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20and%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20are%20still%20stars%20for%20the%20BJP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20of%20the%20CSDS%20said%20the%20issue%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20has%20probably%20resonated%20more%20among%20urban%2C%20upper-class%20voters%20and%20not%20so%20much%20among%20the%20poorer%20classes%2C%20which%20is%20a%20significant%20vote%20base%20for%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20getting%20into%20what's%20true%20and%20what%20isn't%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20will%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Integral%20Part%20of%20INDIA%20Bloc'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20why%20the%20TMC%20was%20fighting%20alone%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20not%20as%20part%20of%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20Mr%20Dutta%20said%20his%20party%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20is%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20are%20with%20INC%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20and%20not%20ARC%2C%20which%20is%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Congress%2C%20because%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20is%20the%20conduit%20pipe%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bengal.%20He%20was%20BJP's%20ears%20and%20eyes%20and%20now%20he%20is%20working%20as%20a%20direct%20agent%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20when%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20are%20having%20meetings%20in%20Delhi%20with%20the%20single%20objective%20of%20defeating%20the%20BJP%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20is%20abusing%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%20And%20that%20is%20why%20we%20have%20said%20that%2C%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20TMC%20is%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20I%20will%20say%20this%20on%20record%3A%20Whatever%20seats%20the%20BJP%20is%20going%20to%20get%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20TMC%20is%20going%20to%20get%20at%20least%20double%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClash%20Of%20The%20Titans%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issues%20in%20Bengal%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20said%20that%20while%20topics%20like%20unemployment%20and%20inflation%20are%20key%2C%20like%20they%20are%20in%20other%20states%2C%20the%20battle%20in%20Bengal%20revolves%20around%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20to%20some%20extent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20popular%20name%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20'Didi'%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20whether%20you%20like%20Didi%20or%20not.%20Just%20like%20the%20contest%20in%20the%20country%20revolves%20to%20a%20large%20extent%20around%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20We%20are%20often%20asked%20whether%20the%202024%20election%20is%20a%20presidential%20one%2C%20I%20say%20it%20isn't.%20It's%20a%20referendum%20in%20a%20way.%20In%20Bengal%2C%20it's%20whether%20you%20are%20with%20Didi%20or%20against%20her.%20When%20this%20kind%20of%20politics%20happens%2C%20the%20issues%20also%20get%20buried%20to%20some%20extent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dasgupta%20said%20that%20the%20TMC%20would%20want%20the%20focus%20to%20be%20on%20local%20issues%20and%20said%20the%20BJP%20can%20fall%20into%20the%20trap%20of%20saying%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20should%20be%20removed.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20BJP%20forgets%20this%20is%20a%20national%20election%2C%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20-%20and%20unfortunately%20one%20or%20two%20BJP%20people%20have%20forgotten%20that%20-%20(then%20it%20can%20fall%20into%20the%20trap)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Journalist%20Nishtha%20Gautam%20said%20her%20analysis%20from%20speaking%20to%20people%20of%20all%20hues%20in%20Kolkata%20points%20to%20something%20strange%20having%20happened%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%20%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20and%20Ms%20Banerjee%20have%20emerged%20as%20doppelgangers%20of%20each%20other.%20The%20situation%20in%20West%20Bengal%20-%20Modi's%20guarantees%20vs%20Mamata's%20guarantees%20-%20it%20is%20exactly%20the%20same%20issues.%20The%20growth%20is%20happening%20without%20jobs%2C%20doles%20are%20being%20given%20out.%20If%20we%20talk%20about%20welfarism%2C%20both%20leaders%20have%20weaponised%20it%20very%20well%20for%20electoral%20gains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20voters%20say%20they%20hate%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20they%20don't%20want%20her%20but%20what%20is%20the%20alternative%3F%20They%20don't%20even%20want%20Modi%20ji%20to%20have%20a%20stronger%20footprint.%20It%20is%20very%20strange.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20experts%20also%20felt%20that%20the%20draw%20of%20the%20leaders%20and%20the%20strong%20welfare%20schemes%20will%20play%20a%20big%20role%20but%20conceded%20that%20emotional%20factors%20and%20last-minute%20decisions%20can%20also%20make%20the%20decision%20swing%20at%20the%20last%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20of%20Bengal's%2042%20seats%20have%20voted%20so%20far%20and%20people%20from%20the%20state%20will%20cast%20their%20ballots%20in%20all%20remaining%20phases%20as%20well%2C%20until%20June%201.%20The%20results%20will%20be%20declared%20three%20days%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714846140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ffv3spq6g_battleground-bengal_625x300_04_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-battleground-contest-of-fine-margins-between-bjp-trinamool-in-bengal-5589210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22West%20Bengal's%2048%20seats%20make%20it%20the%20third-largest%20contributor%20of%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20but%20what%20has%20made%20the%20state%20even%20more%20important%20and%20interesting%20in%20these%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20is%20the%20keenly%20fought%20contest%20between%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-battleground-contest-of-fine-margins-between-bjp-trinamool-in-bengal-5589210%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-battleground-contest-of-fine-margins-between-bjp-trinamool-in-bengal-5589210%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-battleground-contest-of-fine-margins-between-bjp-trinamool-in-bengal-5589210%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20times%20Anushka%20stunned%20in%20designer%20Sabyasachi%20saris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714845845000%2C%22visual