eveloping%20Societies%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20fought%20against%20the%20Congress%20in%20several%20states%20and%20even%20defeated%20it%20in%20most%20states%2C%20but%20it%20is%20facing%20strong%20opposition%20from%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20Bengal%20and%20putting%20up%20a%20formidable%20fight%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20a%20neck%20and%20neck%20fight%20in%20Bengal.%20There%20was%20just%20a%203%25%20difference%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20TMC%20in%202019.%20Even%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20two%20was%20not%20very%20significant%20-%20BJP%20won%2018%2C%20while%20the%20Trinamool%20won%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20minuscule%202%25%20change%20can%20have%20a%20huge%20impact.%20If%20the%20BJP%20manages%20to%20gain%20by%202-3%25%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20will%20end%20up%20losing%20nearly%20seven%20seats.%20And%20if%20the%20opposite%20happens%20and%20the%20BJP%20loses%20around%204%25%2C%20it%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%20single%20digits%20in%20the%20state.%20Let's%20see%20what%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20journalist%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Swapan%20Dasgupta%20echoed%20him%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BJournalists%20love%20it%20when%20there's%20a%20neck%20and%20neck%20fight.%20Caste%20became%20a%20thing%20in%20the%20polls%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202019.%20Before%20that%2C%20the%20dominant%20narrative%20of%20the%20CPIM%20was%20of%20class%20-%20the%20working%20class%2C%20the%20struggling%20masses%2C%20etc.%20Those%20were%20very%20important%20lessons.%20But%20when%20the%20BJP%20started%20winning%20north%20Bengal%20and%20the%20jungle%20mahals%2C%20that's%20when%20the%20issue%20of%20community%20was%20first%20assumed.%20The%20focus%20moved%20to%20Matuas.%20Kurmis%20became%20an%20important%20factor.%20Since%201971%2C%20no%20national%20party%20has%20ever%20won%20a%20majority%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Bengal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20before%2C%20during%2C%20and%20after%20most%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Dasgupta%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20great%20legacy%20left%20by%20the%20great%20Communists.%20Political%20violence%20of%20this%20scale%20is%20not%20only%20something%20that%20the%20Communists%20introduced%2C%20but%20the%20intellectuals%20of%20the%20Communists%20glorified.%20Even%20the%20Trinamool%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20this%20in%20the%20days%20it%20was%20fighting%20the%20CPIM.%20Today%2C%20those%20rough%20and%20ready%20methods%20unfortunately%20have%20become%20the%20new%20normal%20in%20Bengal.%20This%20is%20something%2C%20regardless%20of%20which%20side%20you%20are%20on%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20some%20sort%20of%20unanimity%20that%20this%20violence%20should%20stop.%20Entire%20society%20gets%20vitiated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20is%20witnessing%20a%20predominant%20BJP%20vs%20Trinamool%20fight%20on%20all%20the%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left%20are%20also%20fighting%20an%20existential%20battle%20in%20the%20state.%20Although%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20Left%20are%20all%20a%20part%20of%20the%20mega%20INDIA%20bloc%20-%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20in%20the%20centre%2C%20in%20Bengal%20a%20common%20ground%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20and%20the%20three%20are%20contesting%20against%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20is%20voting%20in%20all%20seven%20phases%20of%20the%20undergoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714835460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F1bi22048_battleground-bengal_625x300_04_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-in-bengal-this-time-is-a-neck-and-neck-contest-political-analysts-to-ndtv-5588719%22%2C%22sum