26quot%3BMrs%20Doubtfire%26quot%3B%20shared%20touching%20behind-the-scenes%20stories%20about%20their%20late%20costar%2C%20Robin%20Williams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ecrosbie%40businessinsider.com%20(Eve%20Crosbie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobin-williams-help-mrs-doubtfire-actor-thrown-out-high-school-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sting%20Shows%20BJP%20Man%20Saying%20No%20Rapes%20Took%20Place%20In%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Sparks%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Sandeshkhali%20issue%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20talking%20points%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20because%20of%20the%20BJP's%20incessant%20attacks%20on%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20saw%20a%20big%20twist%20on%20Saturday%20when%20a%20video%20surfaced%20purportedly%20showing%20a%20BJP%20leader%20in%20the%20village%20admitting%20that%20no%20rapes%20or%20sexual%20harassment%20had%20taken%20place%20and%20women%20were%20convinced%20to%20file%20such%20complaints%20at%20the%20directions%20of%20senior%20party%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20have%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20after%20the%20video%20began%20doing%20the%20rounds%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20proves%20that%20the%20entire%20incident%20was%20scripted%20by%20the%20party%20to%20defame%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20BJP%20has%20vehemently%20denied%20the%20allegations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20surfaced%20at%20a%20time%20when%20West%20Bengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%2C%20who%20had%20also%20hit%20out%20the%20state%20government%20over%20the%20Sandeskhali%20allegations%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20a%20temporary%20employee%20of%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20could%20not%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20sting%20video%2C%20which%20was%20shot%20by%20a%20private%20news%20channel.%20The%20BJP%20and%20the%20leader%20in%20the%20video%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20voice%20was%20edited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20BJP's%20Mandal%20Sabhapati%2C%20Gangadhar%20Koyal%2C%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20that%20his%20party%20had%20convinced%20the%20women%2C%20who%20were%20protesting%20against%20the%20alleged%20grabbing%20of%20land%20in%20the%20village%20by%20Trinamool%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjhan%20and%20his%20aides%2C%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20leader%20would%20not%20be%20arrested%20until%20such%20allegations%20were%20made.%20The%20instructions%20for%20this%2C%20he%20alleged%2C%20were%20given%20by%20BJP's%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Assembly%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20with%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20had%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20raped%20and%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20Shahjahan%20and%20two%20of%20his%20aides.%20This%20had%20prompted%20massive%20protests%20by%20the%20Bengal%20BJP%20and%20snowballed%20into%20a%20major%20national%20political%20issue%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20also%20attacked%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20Ms%20Banerjee%20and%20accused%20them%20of%20shielding%20the%20leader%2C%20who%20was%20eventually%20arrested%20in%20February%20after%20being%20on%20the%20run%20for%20over%2050%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20video%20was%20released%2C%20Gangadhar%20Koyal%20has%20said%20that%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20and%20technology%20was%20used%20to%20edit%20his%20voice.%20He%20has%20also%20sent%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20video%20which%20is%20now%20viral%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20against%20me.%20They%20used%20technology%20to%20edit%20my%20voice.%20They%20wanted%20to%20malign%20me%2C%20my%20party%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20and%20the%20women%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Koyal%20said%20in%20Bengali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Staged%20Claims'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20sting%20video%20on%20its%20official%20handle%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20viral%20video%20today%20exposed%20how%20the%20BJP%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20malign%20Bengal.%20From%20%26quot%3Bmass%20rape%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Barms%20seizure%2C%26quot%3B%20every%20claim%20was%20bought%20and%20staged%20by%20none%20other%20than%20Suvendu%20Adhikari.%20People%20won't%20forgive%20these%20Bangla-Birodhis%20(people%20who%20oppose%20Bengal).%20Bengal's%20mothers%20%26amp%3B%20sisters%20shall%20avenge%20this!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Chakdah%20in%20Nadia%20district%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20Sandeshkhali%20incident%20was%20preplanned.%20The%20BJP%20had%20scripted%20it%20well.%20The%20truth%20has%20been%20exposed.%20I%20have%20been%20saying%20this%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20have%20not%20seen%20the%20entire%20video.%20I%20will%20definitely%20see%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20gave%20sandesh%20(messages)%20regarding%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20but%20remained%20silent%20on%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20claims%20against%20the%20Governor%2C%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20Centre%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Spreading%20Rumours'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Rahul%20Sinha%20said%20the%20Trinamool%20is%20spreading%20rumours%20because%20it%20knows%20it%20is%20losing%20on%20the%20electoral%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20seen%20that%20it%20stands%20no