late-as-shahid-kapoor-reveals-he-was-cheated-on-by-his-exes-in-viral-video%2Farticleshow%2F109843356.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109843356.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShahid%20Kapoor%20and%20Mira%20Rajput%2C%20considered%20a%20leading%20couple%20in%20Bollywood%2C%20openly%20express%20affection%20for%20each%20other.%20Shahid%20discussed%20past%20heartbreaks%20on%20Neha%20Dhupia's%20show%20but%20declined%20to%20name%20the%20exes.%20Speculation%20arose%2C%20including%20mention%20of%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20and%20Priyanka%20Chopra.%20Shahid%20also%20praised%20Mira's%20perspective%20and%20emphasized%20mutual%20respect%20in%20their%20relationship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffans-speculate-as-shahid-kapoor-reveals-he-was-cheated-on-by-his-exes-in-viral-video%2Farticleshow%2F109843356.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20MLA%20HD%20Revanna%2C%20Accused%20Of%20Kidnapping%20Woman%2C%20Taken%20Into%20Custody%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20woman%20whose%20son%20filed%20the%20kidnapping%20case%20against%20HD%20Revanna%20and%20his%20aide%20Satish%20has%20been%20traced%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20Police.%20She%20will%20speak%20to%20the%20special%20investigation%20team.%20The%20MLA's%20son%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20is%20an%20accused%20in%20sex%20assault%20cases.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20woman%20had%20worked%20at%20the%20Revannas'%20house%20for%20nearly%20five%20years%2C%20and%20quit%20three%20years%20ago.%20Her%20son%20alleged%20she%20was%20picked%20up%20on%20April%2026%20by%20Satish%2C%20the%20close%20aid%20of%20HD%20Revanna.%20She%20was%20brought%20home%20the%20same%20day%2C%20but%20was%20taken%20by%20HD%20Revanna's%20man%20on%20April%2029.%20She%20had%20been%20missing%20since%20then.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJust%20before%20he%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%2C%20HD%20Revanna's%20request%20for%20interim%20protection%20from%20arrest%20in%20the%20kidnapping%20case%20was%20rejected%20by%20a%20local%20court.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20was%20this%20person%20kidnapped%3F%20We%20still%20don't%20know%20the%20involvement%20of%20Prajwal%20(Revanna).%20Certain%20sections%20of%20the%20complaint%20speak%20volumes%20of%20what%20transpired.%20Are%20they%20preventing%20her%20from%20filing%20a%20complaint%3F%20We%20can't%20see%20this%20FIR%20in%20isolation.%20It%20should%20be%20connected%20with%20the%20broader%20aspect%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20special%20public%20prosecutor%20(SPP)%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petitioner%20is%20influential.%20He%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20threatening%20people...%20We%20want%20to%20understand%20whether%20this%20was%20done%20only%20on%20this%20victim%2C%20or%20are%20there%20more.%20We%20have%20to%20protect%20these%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20SPP%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Karnataka%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20that's%20looking%20into%20cases%20of%20sex%20assault%20against%20the%20MLA's%20son%20today%20also%20issued%20a%20lookout%20notice%20against%20his%20father.%20Obscene%20video%20clips%20allegedly%20involving%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20had%20started%20making%20the%20rounds%20in%20Karnataka's%20Hassan%20in%20recent%20days.%20He%20is%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance's%20(NDA)%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%20from%20the%20same%20place.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrajwal%20Revanna%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20flown%20abroad%20on%20April%2027%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Karnataka%20was%20held.%20His%20lawyer%20had%20sought%20seven%20days%20for%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20SIT.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Karnataka%20government%20today%20asked%20the%20Central%20Bureau%2