m%20ferry%20window%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662ff577ec0c696569fee5e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20ferry%20was%20a%20great%20way%20to%20set%20foot%20in%20Asia%20and%20enjoy%20views%20of%20Istanbul.%20%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20how%20fast%2C%20cheap%2C%20and%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20take%20the%20ferry%20from%20the%20European%20side%20of%20Istanbul%20to%20the%20Asian%20side%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20there%20didn't%20appear%20to%20be%20any%20other%20tourists%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20the%20best%20way%20to%20make%20the%20transcontinental%20trip%2C%20and%20I%20would%20definitely%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-ferry-from-europe-to-asia-one-dollar-istanbul-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714829222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662ff80110dfcda40964a36e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-ferry-from-europe-to-asia-one-dollar-istanbul-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20wanted%20to%20visit%20Europe%20and%20Asia%20during%20a%20trip%20to%20Istanbul%20with%20my%20kids.%20The%20best%20way%20to%20do%20it%20was%20a%20%241%20commuter%20ferry%20with%20great%20views%20of%20the%20city.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jamie%20Davis%20Smith)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-ferry-from-europe-to-asia-one-dollar-istanbul-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farhan%20Akhtar%20drops%20a%20fiery%20poster%20of%20'Agni'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714829122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109842582%2Ci