%20or%20considering%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20it%20said.%20It%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20has%20proposed%20to%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20that%20India's%20qualifying%20round%20matches%20during%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20next%20year%20be%20scheduled%20exclusively%20in%20one%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20this%2C%20Rashid%20Latif%20told%20IANS%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20refuse%20the%20bilateral%20series.%20But%20it%20will%20be%20tough%20to%20refuse%20ICC%20events.%20When%20ICC%20chalk%20out%20its%20plan%2C%20the%20teams%20know%20where%20they%20have%20to%20play%2C%20like%20Pakistan%20knew%20that%20they%20have%20to%20go%20to%20India%20to%20play%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20and%20contracts%20are%20signed%20accordingly%20for%20cricket%20boards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20a%20bit%20tough%20to%20refuse%20ICC%20events...%20In%20the%201996%20World%20Cup%2C%20Australia%20and%20West%20Indies%20refused%20to%20go%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20the%20entire%20group%20changed%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20became%20the%20champion.%20This%20was%20a%20very%20big%20mistake...%20If%20India%20or%20Pakistan%20has%20signed%20in%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20go%20for%20that%20event.%20If%20any%20circumstances%20occur%20on%20a%20government%20level%2C%20then%20you%20have%20to%20provide%20a%20logical%20answer%20as%20to%20why%20not%20coming.%20You%20can%20refuse%20the%20bilateral%20series%20citing%20the%20conditions%20in%20Pakistan%20are%20not%20right%20etc%20etc...%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20refusing%20an%20ICC%20event%20can%20backfire%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20wicketkeeper-batter%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20information%20received%2C%20the%20PCB%20has%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20selected%20Karachi%2C%20Rawalpindi%2C%20and%20Lahore%20as%20the%20venues%20for%20the%20event%2C%20with%20Lahore%20hosting%20the%20final%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not