E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20hundred%20percent%20authentic.%E2%80%9D%20With%20heritage%20becoming%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbuzzword%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20uncommon%20to%20hear%20of%20ancient%20buildings%20being%20razed%20in%20Puducherry%20to%20make%20way%20for%20brand-new%20residences.%20He%20did%20not%20want%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20architectural%20motifs%20intact%20but%20restore%20the%20place%20using%20new%20materials%20and%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20pictures%20and%20decor%20that%20you%20see%20around%20the%20place%20are%20borrowed%20from%20one%20of%20Francois%E2%80%99%20ancestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeeping%20history%20intact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20these%20pictures%20are%20giving%20you%20a%20deja%20vu%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20explain.%20The%20facade%20of%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20critically%20acclaimed%20film%20Life%20of%20Pi%20(2012).%20You%20might%20remember%20it%20from%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20Siddarth%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20director%20and%20the%20production%20team%20of%20the%20film%20wanted%20to%20shoot%20in%20Puducherry%20and%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20us.%20The%20facade%20features%20in%20one%20of%20the%20opening%20scenes.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20photography%20team%20and%20cinematographer%20director%20stayed%20at%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20during%20the%20filming%20of%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20has%20seen%20its%20share%20of%20fame.%20In%202019%2C%20it%20featured%20in%20a%20BBC%20travel%20documentary%20series%20%E2%80%98The%20Real%20Marigold%20Hotel%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20accolades%20are%20merely%20feathers%20in%20its%20cap.%20The%20real%20success%20lies%20in%20its%20restoration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20736px)%20100vw%2C%20736px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22736%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gratitude%20Heritage%20is%20a%20200%20year%20old%20home%20that%20is%20built%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20French%20and%20Tamil%20architectural%20practices%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229.jpg%20736w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229-300x209.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229-500x349.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229-150x105.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347592%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22513%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGratitude%20Heritage%20is%20a%20200-year-old%20home%20that%20is%20built%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20French%20and%20Tamil%20architectural%20practices%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Siddarth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385-500x667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Authentic%20South%20Indian%20food%20is%20served%20at%20the%20homestay%20prepared%20by%20staff%20who%20are%20locals%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup